        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer39202941" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14358794711657056989">This was the first buddhist book I ever read. It is the reason for me finding my home in spirituality. It is well written, clear and moving. You will learn a lot from this book and it will help you find your path. I recommend this book to anyone searching for a spiritual direction.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


