<div id="review_2871994373" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2871994373" />
    <a title="Chris Dietzel" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/19351209-chris-dietzel"><img alt="Chris Dietzel" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1501356106p2/19351209.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2871994373?book_show_action=true">Aug 02, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Chris Dietzel" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Chris Dietzel" href="/user/show/19351209-chris-dietzel">Chris Dietzel</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2871994373" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16768781477435424761">This was excellent. I&apos;ve read a couple books that are similar, most notably <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/299869.I_Am_That_Talks_with_Sri_Nisargadatta_Maharaj' title='I Am That Talks with Sri Nisargadatta Maharaj by Nisargadatta Maharaj' rel='nofollow noopener'>I Am That: Talks with Sri Nisargadatta Maharaj</a>. What makes this book so much more enjoyable than the others I&apos;ve read is that it is accessible and casual at every turn. There were huge chunks of &apos;I Am That&apos; that were dense and just didn&apos;t make sense to a novice like me. This book excels by being extremely easy to follow while also not preaching. Highly recommended if this subject matter interests you at all. </span>
  <span id="freeText16768781477435424761" style="display:none">This was excellent. I've read a couple books that are similar, most notably <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/299869.I_Am_That_Talks_with_Sri_Nisargadatta_Maharaj" title="I Am That Talks with Sri Nisargadatta Maharaj by Nisargadatta Maharaj" rel="nofollow noopener">I Am That: Talks with Sri Nisargadatta Maharaj</a>. What makes this book so much more enjoyable than the others I've read is that it is accessible and casual at every turn. There were huge chunks of 'I Am That' that were dense and just didn't make sense to a novice like me. This book excels by being extremely easy to follow while also not preaching. Highly recommended if this subject matter interests you at all. </span>
  <a data-text-id="16768781477435424761" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
