          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="ebook 9780385530989" href="/book/show/7010307-awakening-the-buddha-within-awakening-the-buddha-within">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
