        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3658439634" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8010696382332315239">201122: prescriptive, descriptive, not analytic. more religion than philosophy. more ‘way’. more heart than head. perhaps this is the true way to know buddhist thoughts, probably should have started here if i had been primarily interested in enlightenment rather than understanding arguments etc as is i have read a lot of both buddhism and philosophy so while this is very good it is familiar, formal, does not encourage me to read bibliography... but very good in its way...</span>

          </span>
        </div>


