              <span id="reviewTextContainer397598915" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15726710661924887242">For anyone who is interested in the basic/fundamentals of Buddhism, this is the book for you. It is written in lay man terms and easy to understand. THis book lays out all the fundamentals of practice in a clear and concise manner, adding to it a sense of humor. It takes the precepts of Buddhism and places them in our modern day world and teaches one how to begin and stay on the path. </span>

          </span>
